content.warning: Okuva enkola eno bw’ekola ku lukusa olunene ku ssimu yo, olukusa lungi lwa bulabe nnyo, n’olwekyo toziyingiza oba okuzikola nga tomanyi bulungi bulabe bwa katale oba script. Bw'omala okuyingiza ebirimu mu kasanduuko k'ebiwandiiko "kaadi y'akatale" oba "akatale aketongodde" wansi, ebirimu bijja kukolebwa mu bwangu nga koodi. Nsaba mwegendereze.
content.fullMarket: Omukutu gwa yintaneeti ogwetongodde ku katale .
content.marketFullPreview: Okusooka okulaba omukutu gwa yintaneeti ogwetongodde ku katale .
